Class AbstractHashMap<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • AbstractHashMap<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - key type of hash map entries.
    V - value type of has map entries.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Map<K,V>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BrentHashMap
    public abstract class AbstractHashMap<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Map<K,V>
    This class defines some methods and fields that can be used any hash map implementation. Defines default capacity and default load factor for an has map.
